SQL_STMT_U.val: select h.tl_no, h.tl_broker_id, t.tlo_eporder_no_bgs, t.tlo_instrument1_symbol, o.orx_transactiesoort, o.orx_relatie, o.orx_depot, x.ext_id, s.origin, m.external_code, o.orx_detailnummer, o.orx_oorspr_bedrag, o.orx_aantal from trade_letter_header h JOIN trade_letter_order t ON t.tlo_no = h.tl_no LEFT JOIN ordersdetaillering o ON o.orx_ordernummer = t.tlo_eporder_no_bgs LEFT JOIN rekeningen_per_product r ON r.rpp_relatienummer = o.orx_relatie and r.rpp_rekening_nummer = o.orx_depot and r.rpp_rekeningsoort = o.orx_depotreksoort LEFT JOIN holders_per_product p ON p.hpp_relatienummer = o.orx_relatie and p.hpp_product = r.rpp_productnummer and p.hpp_product_volgnr = r.rpp_volgnr_per_product LEFT JOIN ext_identification x ON x.int_id = p.hpp_holdernummer and x.object_ei = 'PARTY' LEFT JOIN order_initiation d ON d.orin_id = o.orx_orin_id LEFT JOIN investment_lines l ON to_char(l.id) = d.orin_reference LEFT JOIN wm_order s ON s.id = l.wm_order_id LEFT JOIN mutationcodes m ON m.code = s.mutation_id where h.tl_no = ~1 order by o.orx_ordernummer, o.orx_orderregel, o.orx_detailnummer
